<p class="v2-structure-link"><b>Message Structure:</b> <a href="StructureDefinition-PMU_B01-A.html">PMU_B01</a></p>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>An event B01 signals to add a new record for healthcare administration information about an individual healthcare practitioner establishing a relationship between that practitioner and the institution.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The EVN segment is used to indicate the effective or planned date.</p>
</div>
